{
  "stem": "20142.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we knew right away that this is-- in what hands we have found ourself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Germans kept just pulling out, one by one, somebody, and forming a column of young men.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was found myself among them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were carried away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were practically whipped away from us, especially women and elderly, and poked with bayonets, with the guns with-- guns with the bayonets mounted.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even shooting and kill right on the platform.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was the selection platforms, quite famous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you were so absorbed with your own self that you actually didn't pay attention.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The shooting and killing of people were-- of-- did not make any effect on us anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was too much of a-- of a-- worrying about-- about the next step of yourself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And not that we didn't worry about the others, but we knew exactly what is going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The screams-- you can't describe this by any means to any human being, to what extent a human cry and-- and-- and scream can carry, especially people who were suddenly torn apart-- the men from women, and men-- women from men, and the younger children, or people who were sick, or not feeling-- or couldn't walk, or had any deficiency in walking and things like this were immediately liquidated by a-- an SS man, or he was Ukrainian, come from behind, putting a-- a gun to their head and shooting them on the spot.",
      "word_count": 94
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I-- we heard the screams of some of the SS men-- don't waste any bullets on Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't waste any bullets on Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Let them die.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we knew that the-- the day is coming where-- the hour is very-- coming very close to-- to the day of departure.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
